OL,5, It is "ridiculous" that vapes are      
OL,6, promoted to children, Rishi Sunak has  
OL,7, said as he pledged to look at ways of  
OL,8, strengthening marketing rules.         
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV's This Morning, the    
OL,11,Fprime minister said he didn't want his 
OL,12,Fdaughters "seduced by these things".   
OL,14,FEarlier this week, a BBC investigation 
OL,15,Ffound vapes confiscated from school    
OL,16,Fpupils contained high levels of lead,  
OL,17,Fwhich could affect brain development.  
OL,19,FIt is illegal to sell vapes to         
OL,20,Funder-18s.                             
